Private command: own task intake and execution order.

You must convert the user prompt into concrete requirements and a short execution queue.
Do not implement code.
Do not run tests.
Make the task clear enough that Architect, Developer, Tester, Reviewer, Improver, and Memory can work without asking follow-up questions.
